title: The Legacy of Elvis - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 11/4/22
itunes:title: The Legacy of Elvis - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 11/4/22
description:
George Noory and author Sally Hoedel discuss the life and early death of Elvis Presley, the rumors that he faked his death and is secretly still alive, his little known fear of flying and the importance of Elvis as a cultural and historical figure.
